First Sarasota Bancorp saidits shareholders approved the acquisition of its CityCommercial Bank subsidiary by First Union Corp's &lt;FUNC> FirstUnion National Bank of Florida.    The purchase price of the outstanding shares is about 8.6mln dlrs.    The transaction, subject to regulatory approval, isexpected to be completed during the second quarter of 1987.    After completing the City Commercial acquisition and fourother acquisitions having combined assets of 248 mln dlrs,First Union will have assets of 28.6 billion dlrs. Reuter&#3;